column5: Got out to Lake O for some spring fun.  A beauty day for trolling around the lake.  No salmon yet.
Nice Work. Thats a wicked laker.
You can throw a few of your "no salmon" days my way anytime! Beauty brownies! Thanks for sharing.
Nice!!   30 KM East wind Saturday is going to ruin my weekend plan.  I hope the forecast changes.  Nice fish!
nice fish greg. thanks for the info yesterday. we didnt get any fish  but knowing what to do helps greatly . thank again
Where do you launch out of Greg? Im putting in at Port Dalhousie this year for the first time.  Im looking forward to it.
Wow, that is a beast.  Great day by the looks of it

Nice shooting there Greg.   PD is one of the first hot spots on the lake for early kings, but typically mid to late April. Who knows with the weather this year? As far as the browns for this weekend, with the easterlies moving in tomorrow, the warmer shore water will be blown back farther of shore. Not sure if I'd even want to be on the big lake this weekend (as Grimace has already mentioned).
